{"tid":2031423,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"仆你個乖 聽日世清同宇清喺sogo決戰都冇人提？","createTime":"2020-05-23T11:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T13:23:23.000Z","uid":234509,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0277c44661e87d9b360d9af946ae087a4a72214d","tid":2031423,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ckVh942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FckVh942.jpg&h=55ba9f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次世清喺瑞和街不戰而怯 敗走觀塘嘅畫面仲歷歷在目<br />\n但宇清三番四次挑戰世清底線 更挾持世清愛妻佩雷斯主席<br />\n世清終於忍無可忍 決定向胡cfu 指教<br />\n今時今日嘅世清唔再喺以前嘅世清！<br />\n更下戰書約宇清喺中立場sogo決戰<br />\n想睇嘅觀眾出嚟銅鑼灣就自然睇到<br />\n如有任何查詢 請致電94340634 搵波台PR專員乃兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e957247045eb33569e6b2261a2965a49fc70c4a0","tid":2031423,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"清深黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d453818adbcebc1c0a0836383440fbbe2f96551","tid":2031423,"uid":348453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a55d9b7c60c2ed7f707bfe3adcd226db907d214","tid":2031423,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">524 港島見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span>"},{"pid":"53c23fce18b865987bcebd184d58bb845887d14b","tid":2031423,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" c